name: Javity Engine
tagline: 2D Game Engine for Java, based on LibGdx and Unity concepts
body:
### Welcome to JavityEngine Pages.
JavityEngine is 2D Game Engine that allow you perform game development process. It support components system and parent-child structure game objects. Underneath it based on LibGDX and around libraries

### Download

Get last javity-setup.jar for fast project prepare: [javity-setup.jar](https://github.com/Radomiej/JavityEngine/releases/download/0.5.0/javity-setup.jar)
or check [releases](https://github.com/Radomiej/JavityEngine/releases)
